# Assets Loans And Receivables Non Current Insurance And Other Recoveries Net Amount

## identifier
de9046

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of insurance and other recoveries outstanding, which may consist of subrogation, salvage or other recoveries. This item is net of any provision for doubtful debts and is classified as non-current in accordance with relevant accounting standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.LoansAndReceivables.NonCurrentInsuranceAndOtherRecoveriesNet.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo5.02.06
- period=instant
